author: @pitgroove.37_66
text:
I still find it hard to believe that BP has gotten this big, yet I was hoping something like this would happen and I'm so happy it has. Even though it's happy tears, these ladies are still crying and sometimes it's very hard for me to watch, but yet I can find joy in these ladies recognizing that all their years of hard work is paying off.

At this point I can officially say I am very proud to call myself a blink, because I've realized that one of the things that symbolizes this group is pushing, battling, and fighting through hardships and horrible moments, not giving up and to keep on going, enjoying both the journey the very people that are supporting you and helping you along that journey, and everybody in the world is going on the same kind of journey in some way as these four ladies and all their fellow K-pop star colleagues are.

I am still at a loss for words from how far BP have come, but it's best to say they're not stopping anytime soon, and their humbleness and character is why myself and so many people around the world love them so much. Saranghae BLACKPINK â¤â¤â¤â¤
